00:48:47,980 --> 00:48:49,970
that it'd belong to a vampire like you.

569
00:48:52,240 --> 00:48:53,690
Sorry for disappointing you.

570
00:48:57,690 --> 00:48:58,910
But you

571
00:49:00,540 --> 00:49:03,000
have always been looking out for me, right?

572
00:49:05,040 --> 00:49:06,120
Thanks.

573
00:49:13,330 --> 00:49:15,250
It's yours now.

574
00:49:15,570 --> 00:49:16,680
Keep it.

575
00:50:55,340 --> 00:50:56,440
What is it?

576
00:51:00,380 --> 00:51:01,320
No?

577
00:51:05,310 --> 00:51:07,560
You're still not going to help your "VIP" friend carry his stuff?

578
00:51:19,390 --> 00:51:21,510
I think you shouldn't be mad at Miss Nuan.

579
00:51:22,480 --> 00:51:23,730
At least,

580
00:51:23,760 --> 00:51:25,820
she has been raising us up until now.

581
00:51:35,040 --> 00:51:36,390
For the scholarship,

582
00:51:37,360 --> 00:51:39,290
I think I will decline it.

583
00:51:40,120 --> 00:51:41,830
I feel bad for you.

584
00:51:43,330 --> 00:51:44,350
Dude.

585
00:51:44,370 --> 00:51:45,510
There's no need for that.

586
00:51:46,260 --> 00:51:47,870
It's a lot of money.

587
00:51:48,960 --> 00:51:50,640
I thought it through.

588
00:51:50,680 --> 00:51:53,300
I'll take out a student loan

589
00:51:53,330 --> 00:51:55,300
and work to cover myself.

590
00:51:55,340 --> 00:51:56,570
It's actually a good thing.

591
00:51:56,630 --> 00:51:58,470
I don't want to owe anyone anything.

592
00:51:58,930 --> 00:51:59,900
Kla.

593
00:52:00,620 --> 00:52:02,610
I'm not angry at you or anything.

594
00:52:04,050 --> 00:52:05,660
Don't worry,

595
00:52:05,670 --> 00:52:08,950
I'll take care of all the expenses.

596
00:52:08,980 --> 00:52:10,940
Also, you don't have to work.

597
00:52:13,830 --> 00:52:14,630
Well,

598
00:52:16,470 --> 00:52:17,670
about work,

599
00:52:18,420 --> 00:52:20,050
I can help you out now.

600
00:52:21,200 --> 00:52:24,550
What people were saying about me being unwell was a lie.

601
00:52:24,590 --> 00:52:26,110
I'm actually healthy.

602
00:52:27,010 --> 00:52:29,560
What the truth is all about,

603
00:52:29,600 --> 00:52:31,210
you can tell me later when you're ready.

604
00:52:36,710 --> 00:52:38,120
Thanks, Kla.

605
00:52:39,200 --> 00:52:41,600
You're my only friend.

606
00:52:42,280 --> 00:52:43,370
Actually, no.

607
00:52:44,040 --> 00:52:46,740
You're the only family I have now.

608
00:52:47,820 --> 00:52:48,850
Sure!

609
00:52:50,070 --> 00:52:51,210
Also,

610
00:52:51,250 --> 00:52:52,850
you'd better show me respect.

611
00:52:52,890 --> 00:52:54,700
At least, I'm older than you.

612
00:52:54,720 --> 00:52:55,160
Go on.

613
00:52:55,190 --> 00:52:56,050
Do that now.

614
00:52:57,810 --> 00:52:58,530
No.

615
00:52:59,070 --> 00:53:00,860
You're not that respectable.

616
00:53:00,890 --> 00:53:02,850
You moron.

617
00:53:04,430 --> 00:53:05,950
By the way, Tong.

618
00:53:05,990 --> 00:53:08,550
The research friend or whatever,

619
00:53:08,590 --> 00:53:09,830
where is he now?

620
00:53:09,860 --> 00:53:11,040
Are you not going to do it anymore?

621
00:55:12,040 --> 00:55:14,500
Have we got everyone here?

622
00:55:14,550 --> 00:55:16,760
I'll have you divided into teams for a report.

623
00:55:16,790 --> 00:55:18,230
3 people in each team.

624
00:55:18,280 --> 00:55:19,760
You can start teaming up now.

625
00:55:37,890 --> 00:55:38,600
Mark?

626
00:55:40,930 --> 00:55:42,190
Hi there.

627
00:55:42,230 --> 00:55:43,800
Would you like to be in my group?

628
00:55:51,610 --> 00:55:53,910
Honestly, if ask me right now,

629
00:55:54,590 --> 00:55:56,350
I can just give in.

630
00:55:56,540 --> 00:55:57,270
No.

631
00:55:58,120 --> 00:55:59,910
I will win with pride.

632
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:02,630
You still haven’t forgiven him?

633
00:56:07,380 --> 00:56:09,320
Human friendship is the most pointless thing.

634
00:56:10,040 --> 00:56:12,310
Unless you want to be miserable,

635
00:56:12,330 --> 00:56:13,990
you shouldn’t trust other people.
